if a = b then say 'eq'
if a \= b then say 'neq'
if a <> b then say 'altneq'
if a >< b then say 'altneq2'
if a > b then say 'gt'
if a < b then say 'lt'
if a >= b then say 'gte'
if a <= b then say 'lte'
if a \> b then say 'notgt'
if a \< b then say 'notlt'
if a == b then say 'seq'
if a \== b then say 'sneq'
if a >> b then say 'sgt'
if a << b then say 'slt'
if a >>= b then say 'sgte'
if a <<= b then say 'slte'
if a \>> b then say 'nsgt'
if a \<< b then say 'nslt'
